<deviceset name="LTC-4724JR" prefix="LED">
<description>&lt;b&gt;Lite-On LTC-424JR&lt;/b&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Triple Digit LED Numeric Display (cathode common)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The LTC-4724JR inch (10.0 mm) digit height triple digit
seven-segment display. This device utilizes AlInGaP super red
LED chips, which are made from AlInGaP on a non-transparent
GaAs substrate, and has a gray face and white segments.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://optoelectronics.liteon.com/upload/download/DS30-2000-188/LTC-4724JR_new.PDF"&gt;Datasheet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
<gates>
